description: This file defines the NoteResponse class, representing a response payload for a Note in the application. It includes fields for id, title, content, creation and update timestamps, along with getter and setter methods.

classes.name: NoteResponse
classes.description: A data transfer object (DTO) for sending note details as a response payload, including metadata like timestamps.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the ID of the note.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the ID of the note.

methods.name: getTitle
methods.description: Returns the title of the note.

methods.name: setTitle
methods.description: Sets the title of the note.

methods.name: getContent
methods.description: Returns the content of the note.

methods.name: setContent
methods.description: Sets the content of the note.
